```json
{
"application": "MESONH",
"details": {
"nodes": 20,
"cpus": 200,
"time_limit": "00:20:00",
"libraries": ["ICE3", "PGD_2.5km_AR", "A_2008090*", "EXSEG1.nam"],
"environment_variables": [
"MPIRUN",
"XYZ"
],
"mpi_implementation": "Mpirun",
"mpi_processes": 200,
"other_resources": [
"file_for_xtransfer",
"pipe_name",
"PRESSURE",
"REMAP*"
],
"commands": [
"ulimit -c 0",
"ulimit -s unlimited",
"hostname",
"ln -sf ../ICE3/PGD_2.5km_AR.* .",
"ln -sf ../ICE3/A_2008090* .",
"ls -lrt",
"cp -f EXSEG1.nam_EXPE1 EXSEG1.nam",
"time ${MPIRUN} MESONH${XYZ}",
"mv OUTPUT_LISTING1 OUTPUT_LISTING1_EXPE1",
"rm -f file_for_xtransfer pipe_name PRESSURE REMAP*",
"ja"
]
}
}
```
